@Comment:	Time is 1:52 , Recording started earlier , but there was no talking , only sounds of the meal being put together and Chi humming. This conversation seemed to occur before dinner. Present were Chi , Chi's Mot , FAT , 25 year old Bro , and 11 year old foster brother (BR2). Almost all of the conversation was between Mot , FAT , and Chi. They discussed Mot's condition in her hand which she thought was arthritis , FAT's cleaning up doo doo that morning , and some of Chi's homework.
